All Implemented Interfaces:
ReturnCodeException, Serializable
public class SwapFailedException extends AS400AuthenticationException
The SwapFailedException class represents an exception issued when errors occur while attempting to change thread identity on the IBM i system.

If available, one or more AS400Message objects may be included in the exception.
